    <item>
      <title>客户增加软件支出，印孚瑟斯上调销售预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/infosys-raises-sales-forecast-as-clients-boost-software-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印孚瑟斯有限公司 (Infosys Ltd.) 上调了今年的销售预期，表明在全球经济复苏的推动下，客户正逐渐开始增加技术支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/infosys-raises-sales-forecast-as-clients-boost-software-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 10:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅赛德斯与 Stellantis 洽谈支持塞尔维亚锂业发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/mercedes-stellantis-in-talks-to-back-serbia-s-lithium-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梅赛德斯-奔驰集团和 Stellantis NV 正在与塞尔维亚政府讨论投资锂加工和电动汽车电池生产，这可能会为欧洲最大的锂矿提供新的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/mercedes-stellantis-in-talks-to-back-serbia-s-lithium-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 10:05:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卫星图像显示胡塞武装袭击后红海出现大片浮油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/satellite-imagery-shows-large-oil-slick-in-red-sea-after-houthi-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卫星图像显示，红海出现长达 125 英里的浮油层，这是该水道发生的又一场环境灾难，商船正遭到也门胡塞武装的袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/satellite-imagery-shows-large-oil-slick-in-red-sea-after-houthi-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 10:02:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电销售额的一半以上来自人工智能等高端芯片</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/more-than-half-of-tsmc-s-sales-are-now-high-end-chips-like-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾半导体制造公司目前一半以上的收入来自高性能计算，其业务的这一部分因人工智能需求的迅猛增长而达到了新的高度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/more-than-half-of-tsmc-s-sales-are-now-high-end-chips-like-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:54:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股暴跌导致新兴市场股票遭遇今年最长抛售周期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/emerging-market-stocks-have-longest-selloff-in-year-on-tech-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国和中国之间贸易战的担忧加剧，冲击了亚洲科技公司，新兴市场股市遭遇了近一年来最长的连跌周期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/emerging-market-stocks-have-longest-selloff-in-year-on-tech-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:33:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
